main event: A missile test was observed at high altitude, moving fast, slowing down, and speeding up again.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 3-4 minutes., The object was described as rounded and silver., It was traveling at a high rate of speed and high altitude., The observation was made by a man in the rear seat of the aircraft., The incident falls under Project Blue Book with case number 330.
location: CAF VIS, 350 MI W OF CAL.
